  "id": "sunset_mood",
  "name": {
    "en": "Sunset Mood",
    "zh": "夕陽氛圍"
  },
  "desc": {
    "en": "A huge gradient sphere wraps the scene and is set to be invisible to the camera. You never see the source, but its colour lands in the highlights and reflections.",
    "zh": "用一顆巨大的漸層發光球罩住場景，並設為攝影機不可見。畫面上看不到光源，但它的顏色會落在角色的高光與反射上。"
  },
  "tip": {
    "en": "Once a glowing object is invisible to camera you can change its size and brightness freely without affecting the composition. It is the easiest way to control ambient colour.",
    "zh": "發光物體設為攝影機不可見後，就能自由調整大小與亮度而不影響構圖，是控制環境色最方便的做法。"
  },
  "engine_note": "procedural",
